# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:17
translate chinese baiq4_11c1e186:

    # pc "My family is pretty cool and accepting about sexuality."
    pc "我家人挺开明的，对性取向很包容。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:18
translate chinese baiq4_496d02d6:

    # pc "I know they'd be okay with it."
    pc "我知道他们会接受的。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:20
translate chinese baiq4_14c40bf5:

    # bai "That's cool. I wish my family was like that."
    bai "真好。真希望我家也是这样。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:23
translate chinese baiq4_641aa178:

    # pc "I think they'd be okay with it, but I'm really not sure."
    pc "我觉得他们应该能接受，但我真的不确定。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:25
translate chinese baiq4_0937f04c:

    # bai "I'm kind of in the same situation, but I don't think my family would accept it."
    bai "我情况也差不多，但我觉得我家可能不会接受。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:28
translate chinese baiq4_1d7e03dd:

    # pc "I'm going to be who I am. I can't control if they accept me or not."
    pc "我会做我自己。他们接不接受我，我控制不了。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:30
translate chinese baiq4_bc6f44b0:

    # bai "I guess that's one way of looking at it."
    bai "这倒也是一种看法。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:32
translate chinese baiq4_a1ea4d5b:

    # bai "I don't know what I'd do if my parents disowned me or something."
    bai "如果我父母因此和我断绝关系，我真不知道该怎么办。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:33
translate chinese baiq4_73a87b41:

    # bai "I love my family and I don't want to lose them."
    bai "我爱我的家人，不想失去他们。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:34
translate chinese baiq4_86bff002:

    # pc "Do you think they would do that?"
    pc "你觉得他们会那样做吗？"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:36
translate chinese baiq4_6d1300e5:

    # bai "I don't know."
    bai "我不知道。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:37
translate chinese baiq4_fd5f0242:

    # bai "We never talk about sex, except when I was younger and they'd say \"Keep it in your pants and focus on your studies.\""
    bai "我们从来不谈论性，除了我小时候，他们会说“管好自己的裤裆，专心学习。”"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:38
translate chinese baiq4_88b89347:

    # pc "Sorry. That must be hard."
    pc "抱歉。那一定很难受。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:40
translate chinese baiq4_38e0c606:

    # bai "They're good people. They're just ignorant about a lot of things."
    bai "他们是好人。只是对很多事情不太了解。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:41
translate chinese baiq4_542b0a9d:

    # pc "Maybe they'll come around if you told them."
    pc "也许你告诉他们后，他们会转变想法的。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:42
translate chinese baiq4_3bc5ec55:

    # bai "Maybe. I'll find out eventually."
    bai "也许吧。我迟早会知道的。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baiq4.rpy:44
translate chinese baiq4_c5724971:

    # bai "I'm just not quite ready for that yet."
    bai "我只是还没准备好那一步。"

